  <h1>BROADCASTING HELP</h1>
  <p>
  Not sure how to broadcast? Here are the steps.
  </p>
  <h1>1. GET AN ICECAST CLIENT</h1>
  <p>
  If you are routing everything into ableton or another DAW, shoutvst has worked great for us => <a href="https://code.google.com/p/shoutvst/">shoutvst</a> (windows only)
  </p>
  <p>
  Another popular client is called B.U.T.T. (broadcast using this tool) => <a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/datafruits.fm/butt.zip">BUTT</a> (mac and windows)
  </p>
  <h1>2. ENTER YOUR INFO </h1>
  Here is the info you need to enter in order to stream audio to our server:
  <pre>
  host: radio.datafruits.fm
  port: 9000
  username: your username you log into datafruits with
  password: your password you log into datafruits with
  mount: /datafruits
  </pre>
  <h1>3. SUBMIT YOUR SHOW TO THE SCHEDULE</h1>
  <p>
  When you are ready to do your show, please <a href="/shows/new">add it to the schedule</a>.
  </p>
